The code is here but there is no debugging info, unless the AWS toolkit prints something.

If memory serves, there was a perl script cli that you could tweak to dump the header. If you fixed up the date/time field then you could compare side-by-side with your implementation.

body:
The code is [here](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/platform/s3/s3_file_system.cc#L404) but there is no debugging info, unless the AWS toolkit prints something.

If memory serves, there was a perl script cli that you could tweak to dump the header. If you fixed up the date/time field then you could compare side-by-side with your implementation.

The code does use `.WithKey()`. @yongtang any suggestion?
